<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>IELTS Answers</title></head><body><h1>DAILY ROUTINE ANSWERS</h1><h3>Câu 1: Can you tell me about your typical morning routine?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> -> Let talk about your morning. <br>When do you wake up ? (at + giờ). <br>I wake up 6.30 am. (early).<br>How do you feel ?. (I feel sleepy (buồn ngủ).<br>What do you do in your bedroom ?.<br>I do my bed and do my hair in my bedroom. <br>What do you do in your bathroom ?.<br>I brush my teeth, wash my face and shower *tắm.<br>do (v): làm, dọn dẹp + N (do house, do my bed, do my hair, ...).<br>What do you do in your kitchen ?.<br>I cook my breakfast *bờ rếc f ợt. <br>What do you have for breakfast ?.<br>I eat rice, vegetable. I drink a cup of water.<br>When do you go to school ?.<br>I go to school at 7 o.clock<br>How do you go to school ?<br>I go to school by motorbike.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 2: What do you usually have for breakfast and how do you cook it?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> How to cook (Rice):<br>1. vo gạo = rửa gạo (I wash rice)<br>2. Pour (v): đổ (I pour water and rice in the rice cooker) (nồi cơm điện).<br>3. chờ 30 phút -> I wait (v): chờ 30 minutes. (i wait 30 minutes)<br>Do you like tea or coffee ?.<br>I love coffee because it is delicious (ngon).<br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 3: Do you like going out for a short walk?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like dog ?.<br>Yes, I am a dog lover (người yêu thích chò). <br>Do you like book?. <br>Yes, I am a book lover (người yêu thích chò). <br>-> When do you read book ?. (I read book in my free time)<br>-> Where do you read book ?. I read book in my bedroom at home. I read book in the library (lai bờ re rì) at school.<br>Why the library ?.<br>Because it is near my house. It is two kilometres. It is only 7 minutes to go there.<br>Why do love reading book ?.<br>Because it is my hobby. I feel relaxed.<br>Do you like to go reading book alone or with friends ?<br>I like reading books with friends. more people more fun. I can share the content with friends.<br>Do you like shopping ?. When do you go shopping ?<br>Yes, I am a shopping lover (người yêu thích chò). (I go shopping in my free time).<br>Where do you go shopping ?.<br>-> I go shopping at the supermarket.<br>Why the supermarket ?.<br>it is near my house. how far ?. It is a kilometre. How much time ?. only four minutes to go there.<br>Do you like walking ?.<br>Yes, i am a walking lover. <br>When do you go walking ?. I go walking after school time. <br>Where do you go walking ?. <br>I go walking at the park (pák)(công viên).<br>Why at the park ?.<br>-> it is near (gần) my house. <br>-> How far it is ? (it is a kilometre). <br>How much time does take ?. only 5 minutes to go there.<br>Why do love walking ?.<br>-> because it is my hobby. I feel relaxed.<br>-> and It is good for health (n) (sức khỏe) = It is healthy. <br>Do you like to go walking alone or with friends ?<br>I like walking with friends. more people more fun.<br>Why do love shopping ?.<br>-> because it is my hobby. I feel (cảm thấy) relaxed.<br>Do you like to go with friend or go alone ?.<br>I like shopping with friends. more people more fun.<br>thích (like, enjoy, love...) ghét trong tiếng anh + V-ing. .<br>giới từ: <br>in, on, at, <br>for (cho), from (từ đâu), with (với),   <br>VD: I am from (từ) Viet Nam <br>I go with friends (đi với bạn).<br>I do everything (mọi thứ) for (cho) my mom.<br>Do you like dacing ?.<br>Yes, i am a dacing lover.<br>When do you dance ?. I dance in my free time or 6.0 am everymorning.<br>Where do you dance ?. I dance at my house or ballet room at my school.<br>Why do you love dancing ?.<br>because it is my hobby. I feel relaxed.<br>It is healthy.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 4: Where and when do you usually go for a walk?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Where and when do you usually go walking?<br>I go walking at the park. It is near my house. It is kilometre. only 5 minutes to go there. <br>When do you go walking  ? I usually go walking in free time.<br></p><hr><h3>Câu 5: Why do you go for a walk only at the weekend?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Why do you go walking only at the weekend?<br>When (?)-> Becaue I go to school from Monday to Friday every week.<br>When do you go walking ?<br>I go walking in free time at the weekend (cuối tuần).<br>When (?)-> Becaue I go to school from Monday to Friday every week.<br>When do you go shopping ?<br>I go shopping in free time at the weekend (cuối tuần).<br>When (?)-> Becaue I go to school from Monday to Friday every week.</p><hr><h3>Câu 9: Do you like going out for a drink or eating out?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like cooking ?.<br>yes, i am cooking lover.<br>When do you cook ?. I cook dinner and breakfast.<br>What do you usually cook ?. I usually cook rice, Omelette. (om lợt), salad, ... <br>Why do you love cooking ?.<br>Because it is my hobby. i feel relaxed. <br>I want to cook for my family (nấu cho gia đình).<br><br><br><br></p><hr></body></html>